c swimmer Ellie Cole, model Riley Hemson, and actor Madeleine Madden in attendance.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 902, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 710, \"end\": 713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"score\": 0.977497500425187, \"rank\": 0.019655499875706174, \"text\": \"Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_Broadcasting_Company\"}, {\"begin\": 749, \"end\": 759, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999320425176921, \"rank\": 5.7701042515030276e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Rowe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Rowe\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Rowe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Rowe\"}, {\"begin\": 810, \"end\": 828, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paralympic swimmer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para_swimming\"}, {\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Cole\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellie Cole\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Cole\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Cole\"}, {\"begin\": 847, \"end\": 852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Riley_Finn\", \"score\": 0.9998077273391165, \"rank\": 0.00017488658256580516, \"text\": \"Riley\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.