rce/Marseille\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"L'Or\\u00e9al Paris is a brand I have known and loved since I was a teenager buying my first mascara and lipstick,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1332, \"end\": 1339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"score\": 0.9987542205413759, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\"}, {\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999140528, \"rank\": 8.59603929463247e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Being born in France, I remember growing up seeing the ads in French and English, and that French connection makes it such a lovely fit.\\\"\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.999376775654934, \"rank\": 0.0005472677148525829, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1545, \"end\": 1562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Connection\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2422352103354225e-18, \"text\": \"French connection\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Connection\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Connection\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Brand Director of L'Or\\u00e9al, Nadia Adelina, revealed to Nine Honey that the runway show brings together inspiring and diverse women who reflect a modern and inclusive vision of beauty.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9999320425176921, \"rank\": 5.7701042515030276e-05, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 1622, \"end\": 1629, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"score\": 0.9987542205413759, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/L'Or\\u00e9al\"}, {\"begin\": 1631, \"end\": 1636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Boulanger\", \"score\": 0.9936479540895176, \"rank\": 0.004507775407505261, \"text\": \"Nadia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Boulanger\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nadia_Boulanger\"}, {\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1644, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelina,_Maryland\", \"score\": 0.7593254532816945, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adelina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelina,_Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adelina,_Maryland\"}, {\"begin\": 1658, \"end\": 1662, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4830743674189497e-22, \"text\": \"Nine\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nine_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For L'Or\\u00e9al Paris, beauty is about more than what you look like, and all of these women - led by Jessica Fox, Madeleine Madden, and Riley Hemson - are dedicated to uplifting and empowering every Australian woman to believe in her own inherent worth,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1793, \"end\": 1800, \"title\":